data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom end row brick home in Easton, PA. This home features gleaming hardwood floors, a stylish kitchen boasting granite countertops, and two full bathrooms. Expansive attic space offers potential for a fourth bedroom. Conveniently located near Rt. 22 and downtown Easton, a hub of restaurants and food options. Schedule your showing today!
